<item>
            <title>[LU-17310] e2fsprogs m_assume_storage_prezeroed test fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17310</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A new test case &lt;tt&gt;m_assume_storage_prezeroed&lt;/tt&gt; added into e2fsprogs-1.47 has an expectation about exactly how the filesystem is formatted (specific number of blocks written by &lt;tt&gt;mke2fs&lt;/tt&gt;), but this can vary depending on the filesystem formatting options.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test case should be made more robust.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
